name: Onion2web
body:
This site is reverse proxy for
[Tor](https://torproject.org/)'s
[hidden services](https://www.torproject.org/docs/hidden-services.html.en).

To access hidden service using onion.gq,
append `.gq` to its name.
Example: access hidden service
[kpvzxxbbraaigawj.onion](http://kpvzxxbbraaigawj.onion) as
[kpvzxxbbraaigawj.onion.gq](http://kpvzxxbbraaigawj.onion.gq).

This machine does not host or contain any illegal content.
Network infrastructure maintainers are
not liable for the type of content that passes
over their equipment.
